Project Structure ( for continuous understanding ):

model ( folder ):
    Holds a virtual representation of every entity modeled in the data source
    for temporal usage  ( pure java class )

connection ( folder ):
    Holds connection to the database ( pure java class )

db ( folder ):
    Blueprint of the SQL operations needed by all entity ( java interface )

action ( folder ):
    Web app router and form validations ( pure java class )

db.sql.implementer( folder ):
    Encapsulate sql operations blueprint declared in the db folder ( abstract 
    classes )